Brillient Corporation is currently seeking a Strategic Planning and Business Process Analyst to support the Information Assurance and Cybersecurity Division (IAD).

In this role you will:
• Creating documents to respond to Congressional requests as well as to respond to system vulnerabilities, providing technical responses to senior management pertaining mobile device security, incident response, and cloud security;
• Manage IAD's Cybersecurity Roadmap Implementation Plan;
• Complete TSA Cybersecurity Workforce Analysis, TSA Cyber Incentive Program(s);
• Complete, update and maintain the Information Assurance and Cybersecurity Division (IAD) strategic plan which includes mission, vision, objectives, aligned to Division performance goals;
• Assist with the development, illustration, and presentation of strategic organizational alignments and transformations articulating the associated justifications and business cases; and
• Develop and update TSA cybersecurity roadmap documents as guiding documents for all IAD activities taking technical concepts and topics distilled for senior leadership understanding and presentation.
